You don't wanna talk
about it on the phone?

00:16:00.689 --> 00:16:01.456
Unfortunately,

00:16:01.557 --> 00:16:03.795
my schedule's gonna be
crazy busy for a while.

00:16:03.895 --> 00:16:06.499
- Oh, right of course.

00:16:06.601 --> 00:16:07.268
- What is it?

00:16:07.368 --> 00:16:08.337
Don't tell me you're pregnant.

00:16:08.437 --> 00:16:10.040
(Hachiko gasps)
- No, that's not it!

00:16:10.140 --> 00:16:10.942
(Takumi sighs)

00:16:11.042 --> 00:16:12.613
- So it's something else.

00:16:12.713 --> 00:16:14.516
Thank God.

00:16:14.617 --> 00:16:15.719
You scared me there.

00:16:15.819 --> 00:16:16.419
I may not look it

00:16:16.520 --> 00:16:18.423
but I'm actually one of
those sensitive artist types.

00:16:18.524 --> 00:16:22.098
I don't deal well with
inconveniences like that.

00:16:22.198 --> 00:16:23.166
- I'm sorry.

00:16:23.267 --> 00:16:25.505
Inconvenience.

00:16:25.605 --> 00:16:26.974
(thunder crashing)
Getting a girl pregnant

00:16:27.074 --> 00:16:29.012
is just some
inconvenience for him.

00:16:29.112 --> 00:16:31.116
What's wrong with him?
Is he even human?

00:16:31.216 --> 00:16:34.222
And why do I keep apologizing?

00:16:34.957 --> 00:16:36.326
- Time to go, dude?

00:16:36.426 --> 00:16:37.896
- Yeah.

00:16:37.996 --> 00:16:39.432
Sorry, I gotta go right now

00:16:39.533 --> 00:16:41.871
but I'll call you back when
I have more time to talk.

00:16:41.971 --> 00:16:42.438
- Why bother?

00:16:42.539 --> 00:16:44.643
In fact don't ever call me
again.

00:16:44.743 --> 00:16:45.679
- Ah?

00:16:45.779 --> 00:16:46.814
- So goodbye.

00:16:46.914 --> 00:16:47.950
(Hachiko grunts)

00:16:48.050 --> 00:16:49.452
I did it.

00:16:49.553 --> 00:16:51.289
I told him off.

00:16:53.427 --> 00:16:56.801
(Hachiko whimpers)

00:16:57.936 --> 00:16:59.707
So that's it.

00:16:59.807 --> 00:17:02.879
(phone beeping)

00:17:02.980 --> 00:17:03.313
(Takumi scoffs)

00:17:03.413 --> 00:17:05.752
- I think Nana's
pissed off at me.

00:17:05.852 --> 00:17:06.587
- Nana?

00:17:06.687 --> 00:17:08.156
Oh, you mean Hachiko.

00:17:08.256 --> 00:17:09.760
Well, I'd be mad at you too.

00:17:09.860 --> 00:17:11.664
"Don't tell me you're pregnant.

00:17:11.764 --> 00:17:12.899
(sighs) You scared me."

