And you say you're sensitive.

00:17:14.603 --> 00:17:16.841
You don't have an ounce
of sensitivity.

00:17:16.941 --> 00:17:18.176
- But it really would suck.

00:17:18.277 --> 00:17:20.281
I was just trying to be honest.

00:17:20.381 --> 00:17:22.719
It'd actually probably
suck the most for her.

00:17:22.819 --> 00:17:23.888
- If that's how you feel

00:17:23.988 --> 00:17:26.794
you really ought start
wearing condoms.

00:17:26.894 --> 00:17:28.096
- Yeah, right.

00:17:28.196 --> 00:17:29.065
Like you should talk.

00:17:29.165 --> 00:17:30.234
- [Ren] But I'm cool with it.

00:17:30.334 --> 00:17:32.171
In fact, I could go
for the family life,

00:17:32.271 --> 00:17:34.610
but she's back on the
pill again.

00:17:34.710 --> 00:17:35.912
What a feminist.

00:17:36.012 --> 00:17:39.252
- And it's all about
what you want.

