- He's not even calling me back.

00:17:48.871 --> 00:17:50.575
How come?

00:17:51.476 --> 00:17:53.982
I guess that was easy.

00:17:54.082 --> 00:17:59.025
Why was I with someone who
didn't really care about me?

00:17:59.125 --> 00:18:02.431
It's a harsh awakening
from my wildest dreams.

00:18:03.233 --> 00:18:06.072
But really I knew from the start

00:18:06.172 --> 00:18:08.076
that Takumi didn't love me.

00:18:08.176 --> 00:18:09.580
(somber music)

00:18:09.680 --> 00:18:11.517
There's no way that I
could hurt his feelings.

00:18:11.617 --> 00:18:16.259
I just finally woke up
from a nightmare.

00:18:16.359 --> 00:18:17.395
Every time we got together,

00:18:17.495 --> 00:18:21.737
we'd go to bed and he'd say
things I wanted to hear.

00:18:21.837 --> 00:18:25.477
And it felt really good
to touch someone.

00:18:25.578 --> 00:18:28.651
I guess I was hoping it
would turn into real love.

00:18:30.320 --> 00:18:33.594
But that was nothing but an
illusion.

00:18:33.695 --> 00:18:36.534
Finally, I've woken up
to the truth.

00:18:38.070 --> 00:18:39.807
- I'll be waiting for you.

00:18:41.877 --> 00:18:43.346
- I'm awake now.

00:18:43.447 --> 00:18:45.885
Because my real prince
kissed me.

