I think his blood type is
A, which means he's serious.

00:19:42.933 --> 00:19:45.370
Damn, I can't sit still.

00:19:47.074 --> 00:19:47.909
How was work today?

00:19:48.009 --> 00:19:48.778
(Nobuo screams)

00:19:48.878 --> 00:19:50.615
- Don't sneak up on me
like that.

00:19:50.715 --> 00:19:54.188
(somber orchestral music)

00:19:54.288 --> 00:19:55.892
- Hey, Nobuo, are you hungry?

