- I told you to come to me

00:20:08.584 --> 00:20:10.789
after you'd work things out with
Takumi.

00:20:10.889 --> 00:20:11.757
- But I did,

00:20:11.857 --> 00:20:12.793
that's why I came.

00:20:12.893 --> 00:20:13.426
- It's too fast!

